  "original_title": "Retirement age of public, semi-government sector employees to be reduced to 60",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Retirement age of public, semi-government sector employees to be reduced to 60",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The interim budget has proposed to reduce retirement age of public sector and semi-governmental employees to 60 years from December 31,2022.",
        "Presenting the budget Ranil Wickremesinghe said it has been observed that there has been increasing unrest among unemployed youth as the government had decided to raise the mandatory retirement age of public sector employees to 65 years and that of semi- governmental employees to 62 years.",
        "He said it has also been reported that the increase in the retirement age has restricted the promotional opportunities available for many public sector and semi governmental employees."
      ],
